						<div class="desc">
							<h3><a href="projects.html">Six Projects Dedicated to Time&#8288;-&#8288;Delay Cosmography</a></h3>
							<p>A series of projects with a common goal to measure cosmological parameters,
								in particular the Hubble constant, from time&#8288;-&#8288;delay measurements
								in strongly lensed quasars and supernovae.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-8 col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-10 services-num">
